Elsa Lunghini https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsa_Lunghini 0 Elsa Lunghini, stage name Elsa (born 20 May 1973), is a French singer and actress. She was a teenage pop-star in the late-1980s. In 1986, she was the youngest singer to reach number one in the French charts, with the single T'en va pas, and she went on to sell millions of records during the decade. Elsa, her album of 1988, had achieved double-platinum status by 1993. Elsa_Lunghini , stage_name Elsa ( born_20_May_1973 ) , is a_French_singer_and_actress .
